      <body>
         <pb facs="1870_10_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Bollenhagen_Hamburg_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>
            <hi rend="latintype">pr Mail via <placeName ref="K00532">St Francisco</placeName>
            </hi>
            <lb/>
            <hi rend="print">
               <orgName type="firm" ref="K01008">BOLLENHAGEN &amp; Co.</orgName>
               <lb/>
               <placeName ref="K00522">HAMBURG</placeName>
            </hi>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="center">Herren <hi rend="latintype">
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L Kniffler +Co.</orgName>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="right">
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>
                  <lb/>
                  <placeName ref="K00522">Hamburg</placeName>, <date when="1870-10-05">5. Oct.
                            1870</date>
               </hi>
               <lb/> Wir schrieben Ihnen Gestern <hi rend="latintype">via <placeName ref="K00543">Triest</placeName>
               </hi> laut</seg>
            <lb/> einliegender <hi rend="latintype">Copie</hi> + behändigen Ihnen heute<lb/>
            <table>
               <row>
                  <cell>
                     <term type="logistic" ref="K01515">Conaissement</term>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>ü/</abbr>
                        <expan> über</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <figure>
                        <figDesc>Firmenzeichen. Eine Raute in einem gedachten Quadrat an dessen oberer linker Kante ein L, an der rechten ein K in der Mitte der Raute ein B</figDesc>
                     </figure> 653/551 </cell>
                  <cell>3 Kisten 150 Stück <hi rend="latintype">Black <term type="goods" ref="K01629">Orleans</term>
                     </hi>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>＂<choice>
                        <abbr> ü/</abbr>
                        <expan> über</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <figure>
                        <figDesc>Firmenzeichen. Eine Raute in einem gedachten Quadrat an dessen oberer linker Kante ein L, an der rechten ein K in der Mitte der Raute ein B</figDesc>
                     </figure>663/651</cell>
                  <cell>
                     <hi rend="underline">3 ＂</hi> 150 ＂ ＂ da</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>
                     <hi rend="underline">6 Kisten</hi> verladen <hi rend="latintype">per
                                Steamer „<name type="ship" ref="K01627">Diomed</name>”</hi>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <lb/> an Ihre <choice>
               <abbr>w.</abbr>
               <expan> werte</expan>
            </choice> Adresse. Die <hi rend="latintype">
               <term type="goods" ref="K01629">Orleans</term>
            </hi> sind von <hi rend="latintype">
               <persName ref="K00048">Bv. Bartels</persName>
            </hi> + werden wir<lb/> Ihnen nächstens sagen, ob dieselben als <term type="logistic" ref="K01584">Consignation</term> oder für Ihre Rechnung<lb/> zu
                betrachten sind. Die Kisten sind durch <hi rend="latintype">
               <orgName type="firm" ref="K01061">Horstman +C<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>
               </orgName>
            </hi> versichert<lb/> + zwar frei von 3% für den <hi rend="latintype">Risico per
                        <name type="ship" ref="K01627">Diomed</name> (<choice>
                  <abbr>Str</abbr>
                  <expan>Steamer</expan>
               </choice>) </hi> nach <hi rend="latintype">
               <placeName ref="K00503">Shanghai</placeName>,</hi>
            <lb/> von da mit demselben oder einem andern <hi rend="latintype">
               <hi rend="underline">
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Str</abbr>
                     <expan>Steamer</expan>
                  </choice>
               </hi>
            </hi>
            <choice>
               <abbr>n/</abbr>
               <expan> nach</expan>
            </choice>
            <hi rend="latintype">
               <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>,</hi>
            <lb/> taxirt <hi rend="latintype">per</hi> Kiste <term type="currency" ref="K01543">£</term> 90-- <hi rend="latintype">Copie</hi> der facturen von <hi rend="latintype">
               <persName ref="K00048">BvonBartels</persName>
            </hi>
            <lb/> legen wir hier bei; indeß ist wiegesagt noch nicht entschieden, ob diese<lb/>
                Kisten als <term type="logistic" ref="K01584">Consignation</term> zu beschauen sind
                oder nicht.<lb/> Ihre <term type="commercial" ref="K01523">Rimesse</term> mit Brief
                vom <date when="1870-08-01">1 August <choice>
                  <abbr>ac</abbr>
                  <expan>anni currentis </expan>
               </choice>
            </date>
            <lb/>
            <hi rend="underline">£ 64.19.5 <hi rend="latintype">per</hi>
            </hi> 6M/ S <hi rend="superscript">a</hi>/<hi rend="latintype">
               <orgName type="firm" ref="K01029">London Joint St. Bank</orgName>
            </hi> haben wir zur<lb/>
            <table>
               <row>
                  <cell>
                     <hi rend="latintype">Saldirung</hi> des <unclear>
                        <term type="commercial" ref="K01529">Provenue</term>
                     </unclear>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>
                           <hi rend="superscript">ü</hi>/</abbr>
                        <expan> über</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </cell>
                  <cell>B +C<lb/>J+C</cell>
                  <cell>101<unclear>
                        <hi rend="superscript">r</hi>/1</unclear> 1 K <term type="goods" ref="K01630">Stiefelletten</term>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell/>
                  <cell>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>u/</abbr>
                        <expan>unseren</expan>
                     </choice> ⅓ Antheil <choice>
                        <abbr>ü/</abbr>
                        <expan> über</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </cell>
                  <cell>
                     <figure>
                        <figDesc>Firmenzeichen. In einem Dreieck mit Grundlinie knapp unterhalb der Zeile, die Buchstaben CG</figDesc>
                     </figure> 8<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>/1, 1K <hi rend="latintype">
                        <term type="goods" ref="K01618">Narvallzähne</term>.</hi>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <lb/> benutzt.<lb/>
            <seg rend="right">Hochachtungsvollst<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01008">Bollenhagen+Co</orgName>
               </hi>
            </seg>
         </p>
         <pb facs="1870_10_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Bollenhagen_Hamburg_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <pb facs="1870_10_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Bollenhagen_Hamburg_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1870_10_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Bollenhagen_Hamburg_4.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>
            <seg rend="center">
               <hi rend="underline">
                  <hi rend="latintype">via <placeName ref="K00512">England</placeName>,
                                <placeName ref="K00531">Newyork</placeName> &amp; <placeName ref="K00532">St. Franzisco</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </hi>
               <lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">(Pacific Rail-road)</hi>
               <lb/>
               <stamp style="oval" type="commercial">
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01008">BOLLENHAGEN &amp; C</orgName>
                  <hi rend="superscript">O<lb/>
                     <placeName ref="K00522">HAMBURG</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </stamp>Mess<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">
                  <placeName ref="K00522">HAMBURG</placeName>
                  <lb/> E<lb/>w <date when="1870-10-05">5 10 / 70</date> 1<lb/>
                  <gap agent="rubbed"/>
               </stamp>
               <lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler &amp; C<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>
                  </orgName>
               </hi>
               <lb/>
               <stamp style="rectangular" type="postal">Franco</stamp>
               <stamp style="round" type="postal">
                  <placeName ref="K00531">NEW YORK</placeName> PAID<lb/>
                  <date when="1870-10-10" cert="unknown">OCT 1<unclear reason="faded">0</unclear>
                  </date>
                  <gap/>
               </stamp>
               <lb/>
               <hi rend="underline">
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </hi>
               <lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00502">Japan</placeName>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <add style="writingMode: vertical-lr; textOrientation: sideways-left" resp="other" place="marginRight">1870<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00522">Hamburg</placeName>
                  <date when="1870-10-05">5 October</date>
                  <lb/>
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01008">BollenhagenCo</orgName>
                  <lb/> Empf. <date when="1870-11-26">26 Nov</date>
                  <lb/> Beant <date when="1870-12-22">22 Dez</date>
                  <lb/> E</hi>
            </add>
         </p>
      </body>
   </text>
   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1870_10_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Bollenhagen_Hamburg_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>per mail via St Francisco<lb/>BOLLENHAGEN &amp; Co.<lb/>HAMBURG<lb/>Messrs. L
                Kniffler +Co.<lb/>Yokohama<lb/>Hamburg, 5th Oct. 1870<lb/>We wrote to you yesterday
                via Trieste in line with<lb/>the enclosed copy + are supplying you today with
                the<lb/>
         </p>
         <table>
            <row>
               <cell>bill of lading for <figure>
                     <figDesc>Company sign. A rhomb in an imaginary square with the letter L on the top left edge, a K at the right edge, and in the middle of the rhomb a B</figDesc>
                  </figure> 653/551 </cell>
               <cell>3 crates 150 items Black Orleans </cell>
            </row>
            <row>
               <cell> ＂ for <figure>
                     <figDesc>Company sign. A rhomb in an imaginary square with the letter L on the top left edge, a K at the right edge, and in the middle of the rhomb a B</figDesc>
                  </figure> 663/651 </cell>
               <cell>3 ＂ 150 ＂ ＂ the above</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
               <cell/>
               <cell>6 crates shipped per steamer “Diomed”</cell>
            </row>
         </table>
         <p>
            <lb/>for your esteemed address. The Orleans are from Bv. Bartels + we will let you
                <lb/>know soon whether these are to be considered as consignments or on your
                <lb/>account. The crates are insured by Horstman +Co <lb/>+ in fact from 3% for the
                risk per “Diomed” (steamer) to Shanghai,<lb/>from there on the same or on another
                steamer to Yokohama,<lb/>estimated at £ 90—per crate, we enclose here a copy of the
                invoice from <lb/>BvonBartels; however, as said, it has not been decided yet
                whether <lb/>these crates are to be seen as a consignment or not. <lb/>We have used
                your remittance with the letter from 1st August of this year <lb/>£ 64.19.5 per 6M/
                S a/London Joint St. Bank for<lb/>
         </p>
         <table>
            <row>
               <cell>balancing the proceeds[?] for</cell>
               <cell>B +C<lb/>J+C</cell>
               <cell>101r/1[?] 1 crate of boot chains</cell>
            </row>
            <row>
               <cell/>
               <cell> our ⅓ share of</cell>
               <cell>
                  <figure>
                     <figDesc>Company sign. The letters CG in a triangle whose base is just below the line</figDesc>
                  </figure> 8<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>/1, 1 crate narwhale tusks. </cell>
            </row>
         </table>
         <p>
            <lb/>Yours most sincerely<lb/>Bollenhagen + Co</p>
         <pb facs="1870_10_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Bollenhagen_Hamburg_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <pb facs="1870_10_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Bollenhagen_Hamburg_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1870_10_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Bollenhagen_Hamburg_4.tif" n="envelope"/>
      </body>
   </text>
